      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and refined performance. This specimen has been preserved with care, offering a sophisticated driving experience and a comprehensive service history. A premier opportunity for those seeking a dependable, high-caliber automobile that balances prestige with exceptional value.",
