    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and is still in great shape for its next owner! It drives smoothly and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend road trips. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Feel free to message me with any questions!",
